{"tid":1908791,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國準備ban疫區遊客？","createTime":"2020-03-03T13:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T20:44:10.000Z","uid":228995,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2192a82b1a11822a9099eb20182c1e7032fdcbbf","tid":1908791,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"//新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續，泰國媒體報道指，泰國衛生部發公告，列11國家及地區為新冠肺炎高危地區，包括香港及澳門。泰國衛生部呼籲國民，在此11地返抵泰國後，應自我隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n泰國衛生部把日本、德國、南韓、中國、台灣、法國、新加坡、意大利、伊朗、香港及澳門列為新冠肺炎高危地區。<br />\n<br />\n當局呼籲，當國民在此11地返抵泰國後，應自我隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n泰國副總理巴威德（Prawit Wongsuwon）早前表示，泰國現時未有法律要求任何人需強制隔離。<br />\n<br />\n公共衛生部長Anutin Charnvirakul上周四曾在其Facebook上，張貼一張有其簽署的公告，指若來自以上11地的所有訪客到訪泰國後，都會被要求隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該帖子在幾分鐘後遭刪除，公共衛生部亦沒有就此事作任何說明。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2580349/【泰國疫情】泰國籲國民從港澳回國後%20應隔離14日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2580349%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E5%BE%9E%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%9B%9E%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%8C%2520%E6%87%89%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A214%E6%97%A5&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=c505aad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2580349/【泰國疫情】泰國籲國民從港澳回國後%20應隔離14日</a>"},{"pid":"40f6d2d2302df07ab6ba1b6d8a5238abdbbcd1e0","tid":1908791,"uid":87642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"星期日去係咪唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bf10f1a41be6b8dacad943307e5f43e6b08323","tid":1908791,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbAyitb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbAyitb.jp